# <type>[(scope)][!]: <description>
#
# [optional body — wrap at 72 cols, separated from subject by a blank line]
#
# [optional footers — Refs:, BREAKING CHANGE:, Co-authored-by: …]
#
# Allowed types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore, revert.
# - Subject: imperative, lowercase, ≤72 chars, no trailing period.
# - Breaking change: append `!` before `:` AND add a `BREAKING CHANGE:` footer.
# - See docs/specs/practices/conventional-commits.md (ADR-007).
